  <md:abstract>This module, designed for the collection of ethics across the curriculum modules for CIVIS, provides an outline of ethics resources available to STEM instructors. Some resources complement resources found in the CIVIS collection while others help those interested in exploring different dimensions in ethics instruction.</md:abstract>
